{"article_id":"iujbbwXVeAP0X7tf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President will end Obama program","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"giving work permits to illegal immigrants ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"sources say ,","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"but Congress will now be given time","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"to draft replacement law","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Donald Trump has decided to scrap a program","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"giving work permits to people","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"who came to the United States illegally as children","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"but will give Congress up to six months","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to find a legislative alternative ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"according to reports .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"What is Daca","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and who are the Dreamers ?","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Read more","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The US president decided to delay enforcement of his decision","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to end the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"( Daca )","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"program","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"in order to give Congress time","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to devise legislation","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"to replace it ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"two sources familiar with the situation told Reuters on Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"The Obama administration policy protects nearly 800,000 young men and women","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"often called \" Dreamers \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"from deportation","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and allows them to work legally .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The decision","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to give Congress half a year","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to come up with an alternative","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"represents a compromise","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"after Republicans and business leaders asked Trump to keep the program .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"They included Facebook founder Mark Zuckerberg and Apple chief executive , Tim Cook ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"who tweeted","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"that 250 staff were \" Dreamers \"","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and \" I stand with them \" .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Tim Cook","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"( @ tim_cook )","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"250 of my Apple coworkers are # Dreamers .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"I stand with them .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"They deserve our respect as equals and a solution","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"rooted in American values .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"\" Dreamers \" are a fraction of the estimated 11 million illegal immigrants in the United States , most of them Hispanic .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Trump as a candidate promised to deport all of them ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"but many Americans have rallied","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"to support the young adults","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"who have spent large parts of their lives in the United States .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"The decision ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"to be announced on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"will seek to placate both sides in the immigration debate at a time","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"when the president is also grappling with North Korea ' s nuclear program and Houston ' s recovery from Hurricane Harvey .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"House of Representatives speaker Paul Ryan urged Trump on Friday not to rescind the program","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and was joined by senator Orrin Hatch , also a Republican .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Representative Ileana Ros-Lehtinen , a Cuban-American Republican from Florida , tweeted her dismay with the decision","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to scrap Daca :","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"\" After teasing # Dreamers for months with talk of his ' great heart , '","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"@ POTUS slams door on them .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Some ' heart ' . \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Ileana Ros-Lehtinen","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"( @ RosLehtinen )","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"After teasing # Dreamers for months with talk of his `` great heart , ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"@ POTUS slams door on them .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Some `` heart '' ...","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Trump ' s base may also be disgruntled about the president ' s decision","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to leave open the option of a fix .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Representative Steve King , a hawk on immigration and Iowa Republican , tweeted his opposition to the plan on Sunday night .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Democrats , such as Minnesota senator Al Franken , also wanted the program to continue .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Franken called the reported decision a \" disgrace \" .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Nancy Pelosi , the top House Democrat , last week asked Ryan to meet her party","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"to discuss a \" comprehensive legislative solution \" .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Treasury secretary Steven Mnuchin downplayed the warnings from business figures ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"telling Fox News Sunday","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"he was \" less concerned about the economic impact \" .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Asylum once defined America .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Now , it stands imperiled","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"|","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Roger Ekrich Read more","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Most of the Dreamers came from Mexico and elsewhere in Latin America .","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"More than 200,000 live in California ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"while 100,000 are in Texas .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"New York , Illinois and Florida also have large numbers .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"Congress under presidents of both parties has been unable to pass comprehensive immigration reform .","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"The Daca issue has been actively debated within the White House and Trump administration .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"One senior administration official described the debate as a \" tug of war \" between factions .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"Daca supporters argue","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"that the people","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"it protects","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"are US-educated and integrated into American society , with little connection to the countries","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"in which they are citizens .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Opponents of the program argue","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that illegal immigrants take jobs from US citizens .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":94,"right":178,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":92,"right":93,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":91,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":164,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":134,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":102,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":5,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":13,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":128,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":113,"right":127,